# TODO

## Mobile Touch Copy-Paste for TREF Blocks

Replace drag-and-drop with clipboard-based transfer on touch devices.

### TrefWrapper (sender):
1. Hold finger on icon (300ms) → copy to clipboard + "Copied ✓" popup
2. Short tap → toggle menu (existing behavior)

### TrefReceiver:
1. First tap → "Tap to paste" indicator
2. Second tap (within 3s) → paste from clipboard

### Implementation:
- [ ] Touch copy logic in TrefWrapper.attachEvents()
- [ ] #showCopiedPopup() method
- [ ] Touch paste logic in TrefReceiver
- [ ] CSS for touch states (.touch-selected, .touch-ready, .tref-copied-popup)
- [ ] Build and test on mobile

### Detection:
```javascript
const isTouch = window.matchMedia('(pointer: coarse)').matches;
```

